{"tid":1622374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係觀塘有個自稱執垃圾既啊嬋影左3個妹豬既相俾人圍","createTime":"2019-10-04T16:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T18:51:25.000Z","uid":212168,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2d2c7d14069dde60da88bf42c577393456c30e","tid":1622374,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:05:59.000Z","msg":"頭先出街散步月行行下聽到有個妹妹話個啊毛影左佢相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個啊毛死都唔肯刪相話佢只係執垃圾 執完要影相交差<br />\n我就停低左叫個啊毛刪左佢 佢仲係堅拎自己無心影3個妹豬  我話唔緊要你刪左影到佢地果d相 之後等無人再影過  <br />\n但佢就死都唔肯又話自己只係垃圾婆 係附近住 不停loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後連塞緊車疑似藍屍小巴佬都忍唔住出聲叫佢個啊毛唔好搞咁多野  刪左相就走啦 <br />\n突然身後越黎越嘈  一轉身望過去原來已經突然有成幾十人係後面 叔叔又有 女手足又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咁幫口叫個啊姐刪相  期間仲有幾個勇武巴嬲到直頭想打佢  我地勸個勇武巴冷靜    搞搞下有個中年叔叔都忍唔住同個啊毛嘈起上黎  仲影返佢相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n我同個啊毛講: 啊姐 你再搞落去只會越黎越多人架咋  到時有人影左你片放上網 你今晚就係人都識你架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後個啊毛唔知係咪見越黎越多人就淆底  話見我禮貌好  聽我講刪相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我心諗你又唔撚係影我相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆街佢一開出黎原來唔止影相  仲拍左3段片  我地叫佢刪晒佢  一刪完大家歡呼拍掌就散水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後覺得而家香港好有愛  只要有手足出事  大家都唔會只食花生  會企出黎守護同路人  當中仲有唔少係叔返姨姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  光復香港   時代革命"},{"pid":"512499e1d1e6b3bea276e6da4eb34d3d0d8e70f0","tid":1622374,"uid":178370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:10:38.000Z","msg":"如果係iOS 係有得去垃圾桶復原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇check到阿嬋係咪永久刪除嗰隻？"},{"pid":"847fa25b99bfcd9078a3a320b1470e2d1659c5ef","tid":1622374,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"512499e1d1e6b3bea276e6da4eb34d3d0d8e70f0","tid":1622374,"uid":178370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:10:38.000Z","msg":"如果係iOS 係有得去垃圾桶復原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇check到阿嬋係咪永久刪除嗰隻？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"啊毛部機似係大陸機黎"},{"pid":"30a479c0ae5b279e8517da37d6cf88eb05ec3b61","tid":1622374,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"60def640ea6275c2575754f7c45a455ffc068880","tid":1622374,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"847fa25b99bfcd9078a3a320b1470e2d1659c5ef","tid":1622374,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"512499e1d1e6b3bea276e6da4eb34d3d0d8e70f0","tid":1622374,"uid":178370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:10:38.000Z","msg":"如果係iOS 係有得去垃圾桶復原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇check到阿嬋係咪永久刪除嗰隻？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"啊毛部機似係大陸機黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"行Android 機都可以recover within 30days"},{"pid":"ebc88a99e6307695688d5432f55a87007c0a3938","tid":1622374,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"60def640ea6275c2575754f7c45a455ffc068880","tid